data.description: PRICE REDUCTION.....Great opportunity to become a homeowner in the sought after Wyncreek Estates neighborhood.     This 3-sided brick remarkable 2 story home has a lot to offer.  Open the oversized front double doors to an open and airy 2-story foyer with a formal living room to your right and a big separate dining room to your left.  Looking down at the sparkling marble floors throughout the first level gives it a luxury feel.    Entertain your loved ones in the great living room with 3 rows of windows and a coffered ceiling that's open to the kitchen with a nice island, double oven, and stainless steel appliances.  The laundry room, a butlers pantry, a bedroom along with an accessible bathroom completes the first level.    Upstairs you'll see how much space the home offers as you walk across the catwalk overlooking the living room.   The primary bedroom is a private retreat that has a sitting room, fireplace, and an ensuite.  The bathroom features a tiled shower, a stepping tiled jetted tub, double vanities, and a huge walk-in closet.    3 additional generous sized bedrooms along with 1 full bathroom with 2 separate vanities complete the 2nd level.      This home is equipped with surround sound all around you.    Look up in the ceilings and you'll see speakers.  Enjoy playing your music and being able to hear it in every room if you choose!  Be sure to book your appointment today!
